Kasar Sin ta ce an samu karuwar kashi 14 cikin 100 na yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS.
Jami'an lafiya sun ce mutane fiye da 820,000 suna da cutar a kasar.
A cikin kashi na biyu na 2018 kadai, an samu kusan sababbin mutane 40,000.
Mafi yawan sababbin cututtuka suna gudana ta hanyar jima'i, kuma wannan yana nuna canji daga baya.
A al'adance, cutar HIV tana yaduwa cikin sauri a wasu yankunan China saboda yaduwar jini.
Jami'an lafiya na kasar Sin sun ce a wani taro a jihar Girka, adadin mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV ta wannan hanyar ya ragu zuwa kusan sifili.
Duk da haka, yawan mutanen da ke dauke da cutar HIV da AIDS a kasar Sin ya karu da mutane 100,000 a kowace shekara.
Yada HIV ta hanyar jima'i yana da matukar damuwa a cikin al'ummar kasar Sin.
An haramta jima'i a kasar Sin a shekara ta 1997, amma an ce an nuna bambanci sosai ga masu son jima'i.
Saboda dabi'un tsaron kasar, an kiyasta cewa 70-90% na maza da ke yin jima'i da maza za su yi aure da mata a ƙarshe.
Yawancin cututtuka na yau da kullum suna haifar da rashin kulawa ta jima'i a cikin waɗannan dangantaka.
Tun daga 2003, gwamnatin kasar Sin ta ba da alƙawarin samun damar duniya zuwa magungunan HIV a matsayin wani ɓangare na ƙoƙarin magance wannan matsalar.
Maxine Waters ya bayyana cewa wani ma'aikaci na GOP ya musanta bayanan da ya yi da cewa "ƙaryaci ne mai haɗari" da "ka'idojin shiririta".
