Bayanai da aka fitar sun hada da adiresoshin gida da lambobin waya na Sanatoci kamar Lindsay Graham daga South Carolina, da kuma Mike Lee da Irwin Hutch, duka biyu daga Utah na Amurka.
An wallafa wannan bayanin a yanar gizo a ranar Alhamis, wanda wani mutum da ba a san shi ba ya yi a Capitol Hill a lokacin wani taron kotun Sanata game da zargin cin zarafin jima'i da ake yi wa dan takarar kotun koli Burt Kavana.
Wannan sanarwa ta faru ne jim kaɗan bayan an yi wa sanatoci uku daga Kavana tambayar.
