A bayyane yake cewa Fletcher yana ƙoƙarin kwatanta yadda Water ya amsa da sukar da 'yan Democrat suka yi wa Alkalin Kavana, wanda masu sukar suka zarge shi da yin fushi a sauraron ranar Alhamis.
Omar Navaro, dan takarar jam'iyyar Republican da ke neman ya janye Waters a zaben tsaka-tsakin, ya kuma yi tsokaci a shafinsa na Twitter.
