Masu gabatar da kara na tarayya a New York sun bukaci hukuncin kisa ga Sypholus Sipov, wanda ake zargi da kaddamar da harin ta'addanci a birnin New York wanda ya kashe mutane takwas - hukuncin kisa wanda ba a yi ba tun 1953 don aikata laifukan tarayya a jihar.
An zargi Sipov mai shekaru 30 da haya na daukar wani motoci mai nauyi don kai hari a kan titin motoci, a kan titin West Side a Lower Manhattan, wanda ya haifar da kashe masu tafiya da kuma masu hawa a kan titin a watan Oktoba.
A cewar sanarwar da aka yi na neman hukuncin kisa, wanda aka yi rajista a Kudancin Gundumar New York, don tabbatar da hukuncin kisa, masu gabatar da kara dole ne su tabbatar da cewa Sipov ya kashe mata takwas a cikin "ƙasa" kuma ya sanya mummunan rauni a cikin "ƙasa".
Bisa ga takardun kotu, kotuna biyu na iya yanke hukuncin kisa.
Makonni bayan harin, babban kotun tarayya ta bayyana laifuffuka 22 a kan Sipov, ciki har da laifuffuka takwas na kisan kai da taimakon rikici, wanda yawanci masu gabatar da kara na tarayya ke amfani da su a cikin shari'o'in aikata laifuka da aka shirya, wanda shine laifin tashin hankali da lalata motoci.
Duk da yake masu gabatar da kara sun kira harin "tsara da gangan", sun bayyana yadda Sipov ya kai shi "mai ban tsoro, mai zalunci da lalata".
Sanarwar ta ce "Cifolo Habibaluik Sipov ya yi wa dangin da abokan Diego Enrique Angelini, Nicholas Cleviss, N-Lora Dicad, Darrin Drake, Ariel Erleigh, Hernan Diego Mendoza da Alejandro Pignoko rauni da lahani".
Biyar daga cikin wadanda suka mutu sun kasance 'yan yawon bude ido na Argentina.
