A karo na karshe da aka yi amfani da hukuncin kisa a cikin shari'ar tarayya ta New York a shekarar 1953 ga Julius da Ethel Rosenberg, ma'aurata sun yi aure bayan an yanke musu hukuncin kisa a kan yin amfani da kayan aikin Javass don Soviet Union a lokacin Cold War shekaru biyu da suka wuce.
An kashe mutanen Rosenberg biyu da wutan lantarki a ranar 19 ga Yuni, 1953.
